text: Wonderful fellowship and warm hospitality despite having to conform with the prevailing covid-19 measures.

Inter-generational worship, infant/children friendly, equipped with infant/nursing room. Free parking on school campus.

Have been attending since 2007.
A community where you can share your life with without the fear of being judged and all this because of love! Some of my life-changing experiences happened thereðŸ˜Œ He is good.
An authentic church community with Sunday service, small groups and vibrant ministries that inspire to learn and grow as a disciple of Christ.
